title = "wait()"
content = "You can use [code]wait()[/code] to stop the farmer for a while. This is useful if you know the plant you want to [url=harvest][code]harvest()[/code][/url] isn't finished growing yet. The function returns Null when executed

Note: while waiting, your score still decreases. So try to avoid using [code]wait()[/code] if you're going for a highscore!"
